Icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19) cyibasiye Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Abibumbye n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, 1 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020
Icyorezo cya koronavirusi (COVID-19) cyerekanye ko hari impinduka mu bufatanye bw'ibihugu by'i Burayi n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, kandi mu gihe kimwe, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye mu bihugu byose ku isi.
Mu gihe tukizirikana ibyabaye mu Butaliyani, inzego z'ibanze, ibitaro n'imiryango y'ubuvuzi byasabwe kongera ingamba zo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19 kuko umubare w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bw'umubiri, n'umubare w'abavurwa wiyongera.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, ikindi gitero cyagabwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'u Bushinwa Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Genzura Indwara cyatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus gisanzwe cyiswe icyorezo cyo mu bwoko bwa kabiri bw'ibicurane by'indwara ifata imyanya y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, icyorezo cya SARS-CoV cyiswe icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ibipimo biheruka byerekanye ko hafi 80% by'abapfuye bafite indwara zikomeye, nk'indwara z'ubuhumekero, kandi ko abantu bose barwaye.
Muri 14% by'abarwayi, COVID-19 ituma baremba cyane bakanajyanwa mu bitaro, naho 6% by'abarwayi barembye cyane bakanajya kwa muganga.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19 mu bitaro uri kuri 4%.
Muri iki cyifuzo, turebera hamwe icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'i Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe icyorezo kiri mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ndashaka kandi ko mvuga umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'abo mu Butaliyani kuva ku wa 31 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yageze mu bindi bihugu, kandi umubare w'abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ubu uri hejuru cyane ugereranyije n'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Mu itangazo rya Eurosurveillance ryo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri al. yatangaje ko ari cyo kiza cya mbere cya COVID-19 cyabonetse mu Burayi nk'uko OMS ibivuga.
Muri EU/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere banduye mu Bufaransa babonetse ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bari bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 yari imaze kugaragara mu bihugu 30 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi na Areeya y'Uburayi no mu Bwongereza, aho kugeza ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 39 768 n'abapfuye 1 727 mu gihe mu Butaliyani honyine hari abantu 1 441 bapfuye.
Gushyira hamwe kw'abanduye COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), cyatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu gihugu cyose ku isi, ushyirwa mu mubare w'abashinzwe ubuzima, abayobozi ba leta n'ab'uturere na WHO, ugenda uhinduka buri munsi guhera saa munani z'amanywa.
Aya makuru azakoreshwa mu gupima COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu kugereranya n'ayo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'imibare y'abarwaye COVID-19, twahurije hamwe imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19, ariko kandi tugaruka ku mibare ya COVID-19 mu bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Reba kandi uko imibare y'abanduye muri buri gihugu ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'amanywa ikurikirana n'iy'Ubutaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
COVID-19 yagaragaye mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu rwego rw'umuryango w'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi na EAC ku mibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 hamwe n'Ubwongereza, byakurikiwe ahanini n'ibyavuye mu ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Ifoto 1).
Ku birebana n'ibihugu byose bigize EU/EEA na UK, umubare w'abandura COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare ukagera ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Inyandiko y'ibanze).
Icyatumye ibi bitangazwa cyane ni uko umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani ari wo wonyine wagaragaye, mu gihe ibindi bihugu bigize EU/EEA na UK byagaragaje ko imibare ya COVID-19 (Ibindi) ihwanye.
Ifoto ya 2 igaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza, mu gihe mu Butaliyani bo barwaye kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe, ku ya 15 Werurwe saa munani n'igice, ibihugu 15 bigize EU/EEA na UK byari byatangaje umubare w'abanduye bashobora kuzakira nk'u Butaliyani mu minsi 3 yabanjirije cyangwa yakurikiye uwo munsi.
Ibi bitwereka ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 ugereranywa n'uw'abo mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'abo mu Bwongereza.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye impungenge nyinshi, ku buryo mu bihugu byinshi, ubu hari ibimenyetso by'icyorezo kimwe.
Ibyo byatewe n'uko ibihugu biri mu bihe by'ihungabana, impinduka mu mabwiriza agenga ubuzima rusange, guhana amakuru mu bihugu bitandukanye ndetse n'uburyo butandukanye bwo gusuzuma abarwayi bakeneye kongera gusuzumwa COVID-19, ndetse no gupimwa.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere tw'Ubutaliyani twazahajwe n'icyorezo bagaragaje ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari bakeneye kwitabwaho byihariye, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko amavuriro n'ibigo nderabuzima byo muri ako karere bikomeje kubikora.
Amakuru y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bo mu bitaro na/cyangwa itsinda ry'abarwayi bo mu bitaro ni mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA ku barwayi 6% na 1%, bitandukanye (kuburyo bw'inyandiko).
Icyakora, bazashyira hamwe mu gice kimwe kugira ngo bashobore gukusanya amakuru ajyanye n'ubugenzuzi ajyanye n'umubare w'abanduye n'umubare w'abapfuye.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-2011 bwagaragaje ko umubare w'ibitanda by'abarwayi n'abavurwa mu ngo z'abarwayi barembye n'abarembye mu Burayi, wavuye ku 29.2 ibitanda mu Budage ugera kuri 4.2 ku bantu 100.000 mu Bubiligi.
Ni ukuvuga ko icyo gihugu gishobora kuba gifite umubare munini w'ababyeyi cyangwa muto ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 mu mwaka wa 2010-11 ku baturage 100.000).
Gushyiraho gahunda z'ubuvuzi, no kuba ibihugu byose bigize EU/EEA na UK bishobora kwakira abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kujya mu bitaro kandi bakeneye ibitanda, ariko ntibagire gahunda yo kwita ku bandi, ni ngombwa ko nibura 90% by'ibisubizo by'ibisubizo bya COVID-19 by'ibipimo bya ECDC by'ubuziranenge.
Kubera ko umubare w'abanduye wiyongera kandi bakagwirakwizwa mu bindi bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, ndetse n'ibitaro n'amatsinda y'abaforomo bakorera mu bigo by'ubuvuzi, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitanda by'indembe bishobora kuboneka mu mijyi yose yo mu Ntara y'Amajyaruguru bitewe n'icyiciro cya 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ibyabaye mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'imiryango y'abaforomo bagomba kwitegura kugira ngo bashyigikire abaturage mu kwirinda SARS-CoV-2 no mu kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, no kwitabwaho byihariye, nk'uko byakozwe mu Butaliyani mu turere twanduye.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo ECDC, hari uburyo budahagije kandi budafite aho bugarukira bwo kurwanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, ndetse n'uburyo bwo kuva mu kuvura ukajya mu kwivuza, kuko umubare w'abanduye ugenda wiyongera cyane ku buryo nta gihe gihagije abavuzi bafite cyo kumenya, guhangana no kurwanya uburyo bwo kubakira mu gihe gikwiye.
Gushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda kwandura by'umwihariko, ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi leta igomba gukora kugira ngo igabanye ubukana bw'icyorezo.
Hari icyizere ko ibihugu bishobora kugira uruhare mu guhuza imbaraga mu kurwanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya umubare w'abavurwa.
Mu gihe ibyo byashoboka, birashoboka ko serivisi z'ubuvuzi mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA, zizahangayikishwa n'umubare w'abarwayi bazaba bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'umwihariko, uzamuka cyane mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19), giterwa n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2), cyahitanye abantu barenga 3000 kandi cyanduza abandi barenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi, kikaba ari icyorezo cyugarije abantu.
Kimwe n'indi virusi, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu ibihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwanduzwa n'udukoko kandi ikagaragaza ibimenyetso byayo mu buryo bumwe.
Ariko, COVID-19 ntabwo yishe abantu benshi cyane nk'uko SARS yari yarabiteye, kandi yibasira cyane cyane abantu bageze mu zabukuru n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'ikibazo cy'umubare w'abarwayi ugenda wiyongera bitewe n'uburwayi bwagaragaye, iki kigo kirahakana ko cyagombye gutanga igihe gihagije cyo gusuzuma no gushishoza ku bibazo by'uburwayi.
Tuzaganira kandi ku nyigisho zijyanye n'ubwandu, ubukana bw'icyorezo, ikoranabuhanga ryo kumenya virusi, gusuzuma, kuvura, kugenzura no gukumira icyorezo.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bitarabonerwa ibisubizo, twizera ko ikibazo cy'ibura ry'amazi ari cyo cy'ibanze mu gusobanukirwa no guhangana n'iki kibazo.
Umunsi mukuru wa Spring Festival wabaye ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 ni umunsi utazibagirana ku Bushinwa aho abantu bose bari mu biruhuko bya buri cyumweru ndetse n'ibindi bikorwa bitandukanye bya buri munsi, byagiye bifatirwa mu rwego rwo kwirinda icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Iyi virusi ifite imiterere imwe na coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003; ni yo mpamvu Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryise SARS-CoV-2, iyi virusi ikaba yitwa CoV 19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, nyuma cyageze mu bihugu byinshi ku isi ndetse no mu bihugu 50 ku isi.
Kuva ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi imaze kwandura abantu 80 000 bagaragaye ko banduye COVID-19, abagera ku 40 000 bari mu bitaro ndetse abasaga 3 000 barapfuye.
OMS ivuga ko COVID-19 ari "icyorezo cyugarije ikiremwamuntu" kandi ko ishobora gutuma habaho uburwayi.
Nkuko bigaragara mu nkuru ya PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed), mbere y'uko impapuro ebyiri zisohoka, inyandiko zirenga 200 z'ubushakashatsi ku byerekeye COVID-19 n'ubumenyi ku nkingo, ibipimo, ibizamini, n'uburyo bwo kwivuza kuva isubikwa rya mbere ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 ryagaragaje ko izo nkingo zanduza abarwayi benshi.
Ubu bushakashatsi bugamije gushyiraho uburyo bushya bwo gukora ubushakashatsi mu myigire mishya kandi yihutirwa.
Urugero, twibuke igihe COVID-19 na SARS byibasiraga abantu, n'igihe indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu mwaka wa 2012).
Tuzategura kandi ibiganiro ku byo twize bijyanye no kwirinda no kwirinda indwara n'ibyago bibangamiye ubuzima muri iki gihe.
CoVs ni virusi zisanzwe zidakunda kwica, zitera indwara ku kigero cya 15% mu bwoko bwa 4.
Icyakora, muri iyi nkuru, dushobora kubona ko virusi za CoV zandura abantu inshuro ebyiri, urugero nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zabanje kugaragara mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Saudite mu 2012, nyuma zigera mu bindi bihugu ku kigero cyo hejuru kandi zigenda zifata intera ndende.
Nyamara, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho, ishusho ya 1.1, indwara y'umutima y'umuntu umwe y'ibanze yagaragaye i Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 mu kigo cy'igihugu cy'ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi itandatu, ubwoko bwa CoV bwamaze kuvumburwa.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wanduye iki cyorezo yarapfuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Muri icyo gihe, indwara yatangiye gukwirakwira mu yindi mijyi, intara, n'ibihugu.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, abaganga batangaje ko hari abantu banduye, ariko ntibasobanura niba iyi ndwara ishobora gukwirakwizwa n'umuntu ku wundi.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020, umujyi wa Wuhan wafunzwe kandi ingendo z'indege zahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku cyorezo cya virusi itera SIDA mu bitaro by'i Wuhan, bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 bari baranduye, 21 bashobora kuba baranduye virusi ya virusi ya Wuhan, ishobora kuba yaranduye mu kindi cyorezo kitaranduye.
Nyuma y'itariki ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko isi yose ifite ikibazo cy'indwara yihutirwa.
Mu gihe cyo kwandika iyi nkuru, iki cyorezo cyari kimaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi (Ifoto 2).
Nubwo iyi ndwara ikomeje gukomera, nta muntu n'umwe uramenya neza niba ari umurwayi cyangwa niba ari umurwayi.
Kugeza ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi ku barwayi 8 866 n'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bwarangiye 4 021 mu cyiciro cy'ubuvuzi butandukanye bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bushya (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UIBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura abantu bari mu kigero cy'imyaka yose, ariko cyane cyane mu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65.
Kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abafashwe bari hejuru y'imyaka 50, abagera kuri 20 bari bato, naho abagera kuri 14 bari bafite imyaka iri munsi ya 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yanduza cyane abagabo (0.31/100,000) kuruta abagore (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 yasakaje mu mashyamba no mu mirima mu burasirazuba bwa Hubei no mu burengerazuba bwayo.
COVID-19 yatwaye igihe cy'iminsi 5 (2 kuri 9) kuva ku isuzuma.
Igihe cyo kurokoka ni iminsi 4.8 (3.0 kuri 7.2)
Igihe cyo kuva ku isi kugera ku isi ni iminsi 9.5 (4.8 kuri 13).
Igishushanyo mbonera cy'umubare w'abana bavutse (R0) cyari 3.77 (95% CI:3.51-4.05), naho R0 yagenzuwe yari 2.23-4.82.
Imibare y'abanduye ishobora kuba yari hejuru cyane mbere ya 23 Mutarama 2020, ubwo habaga ikiruhuko cy'indege cya mbere y'Icyumweru cya Spring mu Bushinwa.
Umubare w'abanduye bapfuye bitewe n'iyo ndwara wari 1.44% (CI: 59%:1.10-1.86%), naho umubare w'abanduye bose bapfuye bitewe n'iyo ndwara wari 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
