Kurwara no kwandura byorohereje ikwirakwizwa rya coronavirus (CoV) n'abanduye, harimo n'abantu, mu myaka ibihumbi icumi ishize.
Mbere ya 2003, hari za CoVs ebyiri z'abantu (HCoVs) zari zaragaragajwe ko ziteje indwara zikomeye, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye cyane (SARS) na virusi by'ubuhumekero byo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS) byerekana ko ari byo biza ku isonga mu kwangiza isi.
Icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyadutse mu Bushinwa mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019 cyanduye CoVs zo mu Bushinwa ndetse n'izindi zanduye zikaba zikomeye ariko zikaba zishobora kwica kurusha SARS-CoV.
HCoV zanduye ntizishobora kwandura mu mikorobe kandi kumenya inkomoko y'izo mikorobe zishobora kudufasha.
HCoVs nyinshi zikomoka ku nyoni kandi ntizikiri icyorezo.
Ibindi bice by'imbere by'umubiri wa HCoV nabyo bizwi.
Kwita ku nyamaswa zo mu gasozi ni ingirakamaro mu kumenya uko umuntu ashobora kwiteza imbere.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe za CoV bugaragaza ko ishobora no kwanduza abantu.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, tugiye gusuzuma ibyo tuzi kuri za virusi za HCoVs zigera kuri 12, turebe amateka yazo n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byazo n'imikorere yabyo.
