COVID-19 igaragara nk'iyanduranyije muri Koreya y'Epfo ku itariki 20 Mutarama 2020 ivuye mu Bushinwa.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima yatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye wazamutse cyane ku ya 20 Gashyantare, bitewe n'uko abantu benshi bari mu mujyi wa Daegu kubera idini rishya ry'Abanyedini rizwi ku izina rya Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abashakashatsi bo muri Shincheonji bo mu mugi wa Daegu wo mu mujyi wa Wuhan ni bo bagaragaje ko iyi ndwara ishobora kuba yarabayeho.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bantu 9 336 bari barwaye, 1 261 cyangwa 13% bari bagaragaje ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje icyorezo gikomeye ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abasaga 2000 bari bamaze kwandura muri Koreya, aho abagera ku 3 150 bari baramaze kwandura ku ya 29 Gashyantare.
Inzu zose z'abasirikare ba Koreya y'Epfo zafunzwe nyuma y'uko habonetse ibimenyetso by'uko abasirikare batatu banduye.
Gahunda z'indege zagiye zigabanuka kandi zigiye guhinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho icyo bita gahunda y'ingenzi kandi ihambaye ku isi yose yo kwirinda abantu benshi kubera virusi, ikurikizaho gukurikirana abanduye no gushakisha no gusobanura abahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima ni ukugeza amakuru y'ibanze ku bantu b'ingenzi bavuye mu mahanga binyuze muri porogaramu ya telefoni, gupima virusi n'ibisubizo bizagaragara mu minsi iri imbere, no kongera uburyo bwo gupima kugira ngo abagera ku 20 000 babashe gupimwa cyangwa batarasohoka.
Mu gihe Koreya y'Epfo yari ifite gahunda yo guhangana n'iki cyorezo, nubwo hari imijyi myinshi yari yahagaritswe, abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari bafite icyizere cy'uko Perezida Moon Jae-in azabasubiza.
Abenshi mu banya Koreya bashyize umukono ku nyandiko yo gusaba ko Moon yavanwa ku butegetsi kuko bizera ko leta ishobora gukemura ikibazo, cyangwa se ko igisubizo cyayo kizatangazwa.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ifite umubare muto w'iminsi y'ubukonje mu byumweru bine.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, buri munyamuryango agomba kuguma mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
