Ingamba zafashwe n'ubutegetsi zirimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'ubuhanzi, ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi, guhagarika ku Cyumweru, gufunga insengero, amashuri y'ikirenga, n'amashuri.
