Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri laboratwari ku ndwara y'ubuhumekero ya koronavirusi 2019 (COVID-19) no ku virusi itavugwaho rumwe nka SARS-CoV-2 bwasuzumye uburyo bwo kwirinda virusi ndetse n'uburyo bwo kwemeza imiti y'ubwoko butandukanye mu gihe cyo gusubiza.
Kugaragaza virusi mu mubiri byemezwa na RT-PCR, ikoreshwa mu gupima RNA ya koronavirusi.
Iki cyorezo ni icya mbere kandi gishingiye kuri RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Gukoresha ibipimo by'ubwandu bushya cyangwa se ubufite.
Ibipimo by'umubiri (bipimo by'amaraso) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima no kurinda abaturage.
Ubushakashatsi bw'abaganga b'inzobere mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo bugaragaza abantu bafite uburwayi runaka, nk'abantu bafite ibimenyetso byinshi ariko ntibigaragaze cyangwa ngo bigaragare nk'uburwayi bwabo.
Umubare w'abapfa bitewe n'indwara n'umubare w'abarwaye mu baturage ushobora kumenyekana hakurikijwe ibisubizo by'ibarura.
Kubera ko ubushakashatsi bwagiye bworoha, muri Werurwe 2020 nta gihugu cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku mibare y'ubwandu bwa virusi mu baturage.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarigeze kigira abantu barenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo bapfuye, kandi hari impungenge nyinshi z'uko ibizamini bishobora kuba mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Iyi ndwara ifata cyane umubare munini w'abarwayi bapfa, akenshi mu buryo bwo guterana amagambo mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Gukoresha ikoranabuhanga rya polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) nyuma y'igihe bishobora guterwa n'ibice by'ubuhumekero byabonetse mu buryo butandukanye, harimo ibice by'amaboko cyangwa ibice by'umunwa.
Akenshi ibipimo byerekana ko umuntu yanduye mu gihe cy'amasaha make cyangwa iminsi 2.
Ibizamini byo gupima ubwandu hakoreshejwe RT-PCR byakozwe ku bipimo by'ubwandu bw'urwungano gusa mu byumweru bya mbere by'indwara.
Nyuma virusi ishobora kwinjira mu kanwa ikagera mu mazuru.
Ku bantu basuzumwe mu byumweru bya kabiri, ibikoresho byo gupima imyanya y'ibere bishobora gukurwaho hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo guhumeka hakoreshejwe kateteri cyangwa ibikoresho byo gupima (indwara).
Kimwe mu bizamini bya mbere bya PCR byatangiwe mu kigo cy'ubuvuzi Charité cy'i Berlin ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020 hifashishijwe uburyo bwa polymerase chain reaction reaction (rRT-PCR) bwo gupima igihe n'igihe, ndetse cyatanze ibikoresho 250,000 byo gukwirakwizwa n'ishami ry'umuryango w'ubuvuzi ku isi (WHO).
Ubwongereza bwashyize ahagaragara uburyo bwo gupima ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020.Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga cyo muri Koreya y'epfo Kogenebiotech cyashyize ahagaragara ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020 ibikoresho byo gupima SARS-CoV-2 hakoreshejwe PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus).
Ishakisha ubwoko bwa "E" bwa beta coronavirus, hamwe na RdRp y'ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2.Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni imwe mu masosiyete y'ibanze yohereje impapuro z'ibyihutirwa ku biro by'igihugu by'Ubushinwa by'ubuvuzi ku rwego rw'igihugu ku bipimo bya SARS-CoV-2 byakozwe hifashishije PCR. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) irimo kohereza porogaramu nshya ya Coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV) RT-PCR ku biro by'ubuvuzi bya leta binyuze mu kigo International Reagent Resource.
Imwe muri izo mpinduka eshatu zo mu rwego rw'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'igerageza, zagiye zigaragaza ko hari ingaruka nke cyane bitewe n'ibikoresho bibi, ndetse n'ibibazo by'igerageza ku kigo CDC cyo muri Atlanta; byatumye umubare w'ibizamini bito ugera ku 100 ku munsi w'igerageza ryakozwe neza muri Gashyantare 2020.
Ibipimo by'ibice bibiri by'ubu buryo bizatangazwa ku mugaragaro ku itariki ya 28 Mutarama 2020, nyuma yaho ikigo cy'ubutegetsi n'icyo mu gihugu kizaba cyatangiye gukora ibizamini.
Uru ruganda rwemewe n'ubuyobozi bw'ibiribwa n'imiti ku bw'igisubizo cy'ubutabazi. Urwego rw'ubucuruzi rw'ibikoresho by'ubutabazi rwatangiye gukora iperereza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko mu gihugu hose hazakorerwa ibizamini bya COVID-19 hifashishijwe uburyo bwa RT-PCR.
Quest Diagnostics kandi yatangaje ko mu gihugu hose, ibipimo bya COVID-19 byamaze kuboneka kuva ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta gihindutse ku mibare y'abanduye; ibipimo by'ubuvuzi n'ibizamini byakozwe nk'uko byasabwe na CDC.
