Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 iki kizamini cyemewe na Serivisi y'Igihugu y'Igenzura mu Burezi. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Mayo Clinic yatangaje ko yasohoye ikizamini cy'ubwirinzi bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yemeje uruhushya rwa FDA rwo gukora ibindi bizamini bishobora gutangwa mu masaha 3.5 nyuma yo gufata, bituma ikora ibizamini 4 128 mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze impapuro zo gusaba ubufasha byihutirwa (EUA) kuri Abbott Laboratories mu igerageza ryakozwe hifashishijwe ikoranabuhanga rya Abbott m2000; FDA yatanze impapuro nk'izo kuri Hologic, LabCorp, na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid yemejwe na EUA muri FDA mu isuzuma ry'iminota 45 ryakorewe ku rwego rwa US.
FDA yemeje ubundi buryo bwo gupima bukoresha uburyo bwa isothermal nucleic acid amplification technology mu cyiciro cya PCR.
Kugira ngo umuntu amenye ko ubushyuhe n'umwuka bigenda bihindagurika, iyo gahunda ishobora gufata ibimenyetso byiza mu minota itandatu, n'ibibi mu minota 13.
Hari ibipimo bisaga 18,000 muri Amerika kandi Abbott yifuza ko byahita byongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 50 000 ku munsi.Ipima rikoresha umuti umwe w'uruhu ushyirwaho poroteyine ya nucleocapsid (N protein) ya coronavirus nshya ikoreshwa cyane muri Tayiwani, bikaba byitezwe ko ishobora gutanga ibimenyetso mu minota 15 kugeza 20 nk'uko bigenda ku bipimo by'umwaka.
Hari inyandiko yasohotse muri Werurwe igaragaza ko "radio ya porogaramu yo mu bwonko ari nk'igisubizo gito cyane mu bihe by'intangiriro, ariko ko ibipimo bya CT [cyiciro cy'amafoto n'urutonde] bishobora kuba mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira.
Ibimenyetso byihariye bya CT harimo bilateral multilobar ground-glass opacificities n'ibishushanyo by'akanwa, inyuma n'imbere.
Nubwo ubwandu bwagabanutse cyane, guhumeka no guhumeka birashoboka ko biri mu byiciro by'ubuvuzi.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwakozwe bugereranya PCR na CT mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu gihe cy'icyorezo, bwagaragaje ko CT irusha PCR ubuziranenge, nubwo ari bwo bw'ibanze, kandi ko ibipimo by'isubiramo by'amafoto y'ibipimo by'ibicurane byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma izindi ndwara z'ibicurane.
Muri Werurwe 2020, ikigo cy'Abanyamerika gishinzwe iby'imiti y'ibishashi cyavuze ko "CT ishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma cyangwa mu buryo bw'ibanze mu gusuzuma COVID-19". Muri Werurwe 2020, CDC yanze gukoresha PCR mu gusuzuma.
Igisubizo cya mbere cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ni ukwirinda kwinjiza abasirikare nka IgM na IgG.
Ibi bishobora kuba ingirakamaro mu gusuzuma indwara mu bantu kuva ku munsi wa 7 cyangwa nyuma y'uko ibimenyetso byatangiye, mu gusuzuma ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri, no mu rwego rwo kurinda abaturage. Ibipimo bishobora gukorwa mu cyumba cy'ibiro by'ubuvuzi (CLT) cyangwa hakoreshejwe ibipimo by'ubuvuzi (PoCT).
