Ibyapa by'akazi bibuza COVID-19
Uburyo bwo kwirinda COVID-19 mu kazi ni uburyo bwo gukoresha ikigo cy'ubuzima n'ubuzima rusange mu kwirinda icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Uburyo bwo gusuzuma ibyago byo mu kazi butandukana bitewe n'aho umuntu ari cyangwa akazi akora, ibipimo by'ibyago, ubwandu mu baturage, n'ibikoresho bishobora gutuma umuntu arwara COVID-19.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima bw'abakozi (OSHA) kivuga ko ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi by'ubushakashatsi bidateza ibibazo byinshi by'ubwandu ku bakozi n'abaturage, aho amabwiriza yo kwirinda indwara ahanini akoreshwa, harimo gukaraba intoki, gusiga abakozi mu rugo igihe barwaye, gukaraba mu buryo bw'umwuka no gusukura no gusukura imyanya y'akazi.
Imirimo ishobora gutera ubwandu harimo abantu bari hafi cyangwa basanzwe bafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura ubwandu bitewe n'ingendo z'abantu cyangwa ingendo z'indege.
Muri ibyo harimo abakozi bafite ubushobozi bwo gukorana n'abantu benshi, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hari abantu benshi bakora, cyangwa ahantu hari ibicuruzwa byinshi.
Bimwe mu bibazo by'ingenzi by'iki kigo, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda, harimo kubahiriza amabwiriza yo kwirinda kwanduza abantu, kwambara imyenda itanduza abantu, no kwambara imyenda y'ubwirinzi igihe uri kumwe n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abaganga n'abashinzwe gushyingura abantu mu cyubahiro basanga ko ubwabo cyangwa undi muntu wafashwe cyangwa ushobora kuba ufite COVID-19 ari mu kaga gakomeye, ibyo bikaba byongera ibyago byo kwandura iyo abo bakozi bakora ibikorwa by'umwuka, bakanywa ibiyobyabwenge cyangwa bakorana n'umuntu wafashwe cyangwa ushobora kuba afite COVID-19.
Ibikoresho by'ingenzi by'umutekano ku bakozi harimo ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi nk'icyumba kirimo umwuka mwiza, n'ibikoresho by'isuku bijyanye n'akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora guteza impungenge z'uburwayi mu kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutagira aho bakorera kubera ko barwaye, kubera ko bashaka kwita ku bandi, cyangwa kubera gutinya kwandura.
Ibicuruzwa bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'ibicuruzwa bicuruzwa, uburyo bwo kubibona (urugero, kugura mu gihe cy'ubukonje, cyangwa abantu babikuye mu ngo cyangwa mu modoka).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibicuruzwa mu bihugu byazahajwe na COVID-19 bishobora guhagarara. Gahunda yo gutegura cyangwa kwisubiza bishobora kuba ingirakamaro mu kurinda ibikorwa.
Porogaramu zirwanya ibintu byose bibangamiye ubuzima bw'abantu mu kazi, urugero nk'ubwibone, ibintu bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ibyago byinshi byo kwibasirwa n'uburwayi mu rugo no mu muryango, n'ibindi bintu bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ibyago byinshi byo gukora ibikorwa by'urugomo, urugero nko gufatwa ku ngufu cyangwa kurwara indwara runaka.
Batanze kandi ingamba zo kugabanya ibyago, hamwe na gahunda yo kwirinda kubera ibimenyetso by'indwara.
Gahunda yo guhangana n'indwara z'ibyorezo ishobora gukorerwa mu nzego z'igihugu cyangwa z'ibanze.
Ingamba zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo zirimo gukumira indwara ku bakozi, abantu bita ku bandi bafite ibyago byo kwandura indwara zimwe na zimwe, gukomeza ubucuruzi, no kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura izindi ndwara mu bihe bimwe na bimwe by'ubuzima bwabo.
Kurwara mu baturage aho ubucuruzi bukorerwa, bigira ingaruka ku buryo bwo kwirinda.
Gahunda yo kurwanya ibyago ni uburyo bukoreshwa mu nzego z'ubuzima n'ubuzima kugira ngo abantu bashobore guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ibyago kandi bagire icyo bageraho.
Mu gihe udashobora kwirinda ibyago bya COVID-19, ingamba z'ingenzi ni ukugenzura aba-ingénieur, hakurikiraho kugenzura imirimo, hanyuma kugenzura ibikoresho.
Ingufu za tekiniki zashingiye ku kuba abakozi bashobora guhangana n'ibyago bijyanye n'akazi bitagendeye ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bishobora kuba inzira nziza yo gukemura ibibazo.
Impanuka zo mu kazi ni impinduka mu mikorere y'akazi cyangwa ibibazo by'akazi bishobora gutuma umukozi cyangwa umukoresha ahangayika.
Kwirinda mu buryo bw'umubiri (PPE) ni ingenzi cyane mu bikorwa by'ubwirinzi n'ubw'ubushakashatsi bw'abahanga, ariko bishobora no gukoreshwa mu nzego z'ubugenzuzi.
Buri gikoresho cya PPE kigomba guhitamo bitewe n'ibyago byacyo ku muntu ukigendaho, kirimo ibintu by'ingenzi (urugero nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka), cyambaye neza kandi gipfutse, cyasuzumwe, cyakagenzurwa, cyagukanwa, kandi kigomba guhinduka mu gihe gikenewe, gikorerwa mu buryo bw'ibanze, gikorerwamo isuku, gikorwamo isuku cyangwa gikorerwamo ibintu by'ubwoko butandukanye.
Dukurikije ibivugwa n'ikigo cyo muri Amerika cyita ku mutekano n'ubuzima (OSHA), ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi budafite ibimenyetso bifatika bishobora gutuma abantu batagira aho bahurira n'abandi bakozi.
Uburyo bwambere bwo kwirinda indwara bwasabwe mu kazi ka buri munsi ni ugukaraba intoki neza kandi buri gihe, gusaba abakozi kuguma mu rugo igihe barwaye, gukaraba mu myanya y'ubuhumekero binyuze mu kwambara isutiye n'isutiye, guha ibitambaro n'imiti yo kwirinda kwandura, gutegura guhinduranya imyanya y'umubiri cyangwa intoki igihe bibaye ngombwa, kwica udukingirizo ku bakozi batatu bakoresha ibikoresho cyangwa ibikoresho by'abandi, no gusukura no gusukura aho bakorera.
Kumenya no kwirinda abantu banduye ni ingamba y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abatangabuhamya n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima no kurwanya indwara (CDC) cyasabye ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero nk'uburwayi batajya mu rugo keretse igihe barwaye cyane, barwaye cyane, cyangwa barwaye izindi ndwara, kandi nyuma y'amasaha 24 nta muti wabagenewe cyangwa indi ndwara, kandi ko batagomba kujya mu rugo kubera uburwayi bukomeye, bakagombye guha konji abakozi barwaye kugira ngo bitabe umurwayi wabo, kandi abakozi bagomba gukurikiza aya mategeko.
Nk'uko bitangazwa na OSHA, ibikorwa by'ubuziranenge bibujijwe ku bantu bagomba kuba bari kure y'abantu bagera kuri metero imwe n'igice (1.8 m) bafite cyangwa bashobora kuba bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'uko abantu bagiye mu bikorwa by'ubucuruzi, cyangwa se bitewe n'uko umuntu uherutse kujya mu mahanga yagaragaje ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
