Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu zateguwe mu rwego rwo gufasha abantu kumenya amakuru ajyanye n'icyorezo cya coronavirus cya 2019-20 cya coronavirus, nk'uburyo bwo kumenya abantu ("abakozi") bashobora kuba baragiranye imishyikirano n'umuntu ufite ubwandu.
Hari n'izindi porogaramu nyinshi z'ikoranabuhanga zagiyeho cyangwa zirimo gukorerwa, zishyigikiwe na leta cyangwa izindi nzego z'ibanze.
Ibisobanuro by'uburyo bwo gusobanura porogaramu z'isosiyete y'itumanaho byamaze gushyirwa ahagaragara.
Ikibazo cyo kwizerana cyatangiye kuvuka, cyane cyane bitewe nuburyo bwihariye bwo kumenya aho abantu bari muri porogaramu.
Uburyo bwo guhana amakuru bukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo wirinde guhura n'izindi telefoni.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje icyarimwe ko bizashyiraho uburyo bwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth ku bikoresho bya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa, harimo na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu igenewe gufasha abaturage kumenya niba hari abantu bafite COVID-19 bagaragaweho n'ubwandu.
Abantu bakoresha ubu buryo mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa.Mu gihugu cya Singapore, hari porogaramu ya TraceTogether.
Abashinzwe itumanaho mu baturage bakoze iyi porogaramu, ikaba igaragara nk'igitabo cy'ubuntu kandi igenewe leta. Muri Macedonia hari porogaramu ikoresha Bluetooth yitwa "StopKorona!", igaragaza ibyago byo guhura n'abantu banduye kandi igatanga ibisubizo byihuse ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Iyi application yakoreshejwe n'ibigo by'ubumenyi n'ikoranabuhanga by'ubuzima.
Ku ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu izaba ifite ububiko bwemewe bwo gufungura Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gupima abantu bari mu cyiciro cy'indwara, izaba iriho mu gihe cy'icyumweru. Porogaramu nk'iyo yarangije gukorwa muri Irilande, no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na New Zealand barimo kureba uburyo bwo gukurikirana ubufasha bwa TraceTogether Singapore na BlueTrace. Uburusiya buteganya gushyiraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana abarwayi ba COVID-19 i Moscow, kugira ngo bumve neza abarwayi batava mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu mu by'umutekano wo mu ikoranabuhanga muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ko hari impungenge z'uko porogaramu ishobora gukora, urugero nko kugaragaza ko umuntu afite ubumuga ariko atari we, kandi ko ishobora kuba yanduye mu gihe yaba ikorewe abantu bake.
Mu rwego rwo kwirinda ibibazo by'ubwisanzure bwo kubona porogaramu za "coronavirus" zitari iz'ukuri cyangwa z'amahomvu, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku buryo ibigo bishobora gushyira porogaramu zirimo coronavirus mu bubiko bwabyo, ikazibuza "kwandika" cyangwa gukora ibikorwa byemewe.
Google na Amazon byatanze ubuhamya bw'uko iki kibazo cyarangiye.
Abashinzwe umutekano bagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye no kurinda abantu bose bakoresheje porogaramu za coronavirus, cyane cyane ku buryo bwo kwirinda bwagaragajwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda icyorezo cya coronavirus mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 yahagurukije impaka ku bibazo by'ubutegetsi.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu atangaza ko hari impungenge ku mikorere ya leta:
igenzura rishobora kuba "ryoroheje, ryumvikana kandi ry'ingirakamaro";
gukurikirana ibikorwa by'ubucukuzi no gucunga umutekano nk'uko biteganywa n'amategeko;
Gukora no gutanga amakuru birimo kubangamira gahunda yo kwirinda COVID-19.
amakuru y'ubuzima n'izina ry'umuntu bizakorwa mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga kandi bizagaragazwa mu buryo bw'ibimenyetso;
