uburyo bwo kugenzura ibijyanye n'ibibazo by'abaturage n'ibisubizo by'ibibazo;
Abantu bose bari muri ubwo buryo bwo gukoresha "abakozi ba serivisi" bagomba guhuzwa, nk'abavoka mu buvuzi n'imiryango y'abashinzwe umutekano.Ihuriro rya German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na Reporters sans Frontieres (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) nabo bashyizeho amabwiriza.
